{"tid":583201,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"巴黎主帥警告皇馬：你不知道將在巴黎遭遇什麼！","createTime":"2018-03-06T21:31:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-07T01:32:00.000Z","uid":25345,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f74c85952b1748fddd68a36a2b9ea39d367164d5","tid":583201,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T21:31:25.000Z","msg":"巴黎主帥埃梅里<br />\n<br />\n巴黎聖日耳曼已經做好準備，迎戰與皇馬的次回合交鋒，主教練埃梅里也向自己的球迷發出號召，表示將展現大巴黎的風采。<br />\n<br />\n巴黎即將在主場迎來跟皇馬、馬賽的兩場關鍵比賽。埃梅里通過自己的官方賬號，寫下了一段鼓舞士氣的言論。他說：「在本賽季大部分的比賽里，我們都展現了我們的實力，尤其在巴黎王子公園球場，我們感覺到一股強大的力量，正如本賽季主場進行了17場比賽，我們全都取得了勝利。」<br />\n<br />\n「皇馬知道他們將前往巴黎比賽，但是他們不知道他們將會面臨什麼。對球迷而言，將有場重大的比賽，球迷也將在背後支持我們。我們的球隊具有奉獻精神，十分專註，但是他們會在這兩場比賽，更加專註，更有奉獻精神。」<br />\n<br />\n「我們將在比賽里全身心投入，我們不考慮過去或者未來，只考慮我們眼前的這場比賽。自從巴黎聖日耳曼成立以來，我們在主場擊敗馬賽超過了20次。經歷了幾天的休息之後，我們將捲土重來，團結一致。我們只考慮巴黎王子公園球場，我們的主場，我們將捍衛他到最後一刻，3月6日的比賽。將載入巴黎聖日耳曼的歷史。巴黎加油！」"},{"pid":"13fe8f5deaede451cb38a33cfe2ffc8b20d055ee","tid":583201,"uid":47783,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T21:32:44.000Z","msg":"愛美麗都進入巴黎既歷史了"},{"pid":"9144a001cd321a3bc4c0398ffa24a4c6d007b1f8","tid":583201,"uid":56847,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T21:33:14.000Z","msg":"遭遇勝利<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd7aec401c45e888dc83b1c0cad151bec42f7cbe","tid":583201,"uid":15993,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T21:34:07.000Z","msg":"永遠唔知贏到幾多球"},{"pid":"9e2de00a76ee8b4ed44b72c78b45b07a12414492","tid":583201,"uid":12360,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T21:36:38.000Z","msg":"係自己半場放咁大煙邊有人估到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8e7bfaed908a9b0fea6422ae4e57d416a40238a","tid":583201,"uid":16846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T21:37:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23ef9a3eb135f0781be560974e46dc55fe43de91","tid":583201,"uid":6577,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T21:39:03.000Z","msg":"咁又係 邊會估到仲輕鬆過對愛斯賓奴"},{"pid":"211c88dd40da772285942d3f54c54eec4a4b01b4","tid":583201,"uid":14497,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"9e2de00a76ee8b4ed44b72c78b45b07a12414492","tid":583201,"uid":12360,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T21:36:38.000Z","msg":"係自己半場放咁大煙邊有人估到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T00:14:28.000Z","msg":"皇馬：哇 你班撚樣燒自己半場 點估到"},{"pid":"6f812012619e2fa7e58bca8b798d959d709644ec","tid":583201,"uid":19126,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T00:40:46.000Z","msg":"講到個主場好似有原力加持既大巴黎炒左賤種皇幾多球出線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"738529feec7e258e8d6f439e1aaeb47ff9fbed1f","tid":583201,"uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T00:41:59.000Z","msg":"煙花"},{"pid":"086cb8e9a3ce26f6bcdec930d8197085ac8b1506","tid":583201,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"738529feec7e258e8d6f439e1aaeb47ff9fbed1f","tid":583201,"uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T00:41:59.000Z","msg":"煙花"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T01:05:18.000Z","msg":"原來係煙花<br />\n西甲真係好少遇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b854a7d582b8480aee60dcb414c056845ff6408","tid":583201,"uid":34468,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T01:16:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">自從巴黎聖日耳曼成立以來，我們在主場擊敗馬賽超過了20次。</span><br />\n<br />\n馬賽都拎出嚟講，唔知以為巴塞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c52c5c379ff704c28b161bd77368437966388efd","tid":583201,"uid":87737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T01:32:00.000Z","msg":"自己球迷玩殘自己，真係估唔到"}]}